      "description": "For sale is a reliable daily driver in fair condition. While the car runs and drives, it shows its age with several cosmetic blemishes, including some minor dents and clear coat peeling on the hood. Mechanically, the engine is sound, but the suspension is starting to feel soft and will likely need attention in the coming year. The interior is functional but has noticeable wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
