      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. This chassis is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully serviced for optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throw and mechanical feedback, driving power through a variable M differential lock. This vehicle features documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. Presented in concours-level condition with original paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a purist-spec machine with no mechanical compromises.",
