      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a rare find for the discerning enthusiast. The Guards Red exterior retains a deep, glass-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the Black leather interior remains in an impeccable state, still carrying that distinct factory scent; the seat bolsters are firm, and every tactile surface\u2014from the GT Sport steering wheel to the brushed aluminum trim\u2014is flawless. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized Porsche centers with a comprehensive file documenting every maintenance interval. Garage-kept under a soft indoor cover and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title, this is a turnkey acquisition for a collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
